==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Ciconiiformes
<hw>Ciconiiformes</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>an order of chiefly tropical
marsh-dwelling fish-eating wading birds with long legs and bills and
(except for flamingos) unwebbed feet, including the herons; storks;
spoonbills; flamingos; and ibises.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> order <ord>Ciconiiformes</ord>.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Cicurate</ent>⟦br⟧
